          "text": "in recent years = 近年\nExample: In recent years, restaurants have taken on new social roles.\n（近年，餐廳承擔了新的社會角色。）\n\nquietly taken on a new role = 悄悄承擔新角色\nExample: Coffee shops have quietly taken on a new role as informal study spaces.\n（咖啡店悄悄承擔了非正式學習空間的新角色。）\n\nthis trend may appear understandable at first glance = 這趨勢乍看可以理解\nExample: This trend may appear understandable at first glance, but it creates serious problems.\n（這趨勢乍看可以理解，但會造成嚴重問題。）\n\nin my view = 在我看來\nExample: In my view, this practice should not be accepted as normal.\n（在我看來，這做法不應被視為正常。）\n\nshould not be accepted as normal = 不應被接受為正常做法\nExample: Occupying tables for private lessons should not be accepted as normal.\n（佔用餐桌進行私人補習不應被接受為正常做法。）\n\nfirst = 首先\nExample: First, using restaurants as tutorial venues is unfair to businesses.\n（首先，把餐廳當作補習場地對商戶不公平。）\n\nmoreover = 此外\nExample: Moreover, this habit damages the wider social environment.\n（此外，這習慣損害更廣泛的社會環境。）\n\nadmittedly = 誠然；無可否認\nExample: Admittedly, some students lack quiet homes.\n（誠然，有些學生家中缺乏安靜環境。）\n\nnevertheless = 然而；儘管如此\nExample: Nevertheless, restaurants should not be expected to fill the gap for free.\n（然而，餐廳不應被期望免費填補這個缺口。）\n\nin other words = 換言之\nExample: In other words, the practice relieves pressure for a few people but worsens a wider problem.\n（換言之，這做法為少數人減壓，卻惡化更大的問題。）\n\nin conclusion = 總而言之\nExample: In conclusion, eateries should not be treated as long-stay tutorial venues.\n（總而言之，食肆不應被當作長時間補習場地。）\n\nif we truly care about = 如果我們真正關心……\nExample: If we truly care about education and civic responsibility, we need proper learning spaces.\n（如果我們真正關心教育和公民責任，就需要合適的學習空間。）"
